platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Maze and hidden object genres blend together in Labyrinth City as you guide a French detective through increasingly bizarre crowded spaces. We love the delightful art style and barrage of visual surprises at every turn—we’re still laughing about that time a ridiculously large banana dropped out of a fruit truck. Don’t forget to take your time. The journey is more important than the destination, as this cheery adventure doubles as a celebration of the vibrancy and diversity of city life and the helpfulness of strangers.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 迷路を攻略して秘宝を取り戻そう
